{"type":null,"faqId":38511,"title":"开启位置服务","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在使用地图或导航类应用前，请先开启手机的位置服务功能，允许网络获取您的位置信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125545\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“定位服务”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“访问我的位置信息”开关，开启位置服务。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>点击“定位模式”，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>点击“准确度高”，使用 GPS、WLAN 和移动网络定位。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>点击“耗电量低”，使用 WLAN 和移动网络估测位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>点击“仅限设备”，使用 GPS 精确定位。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":1,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3791","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441448686000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":100,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"开启位置服务","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}